title: Gaggenau Vario 200 Series 12inch Gas Cooktop VG 232 214 CA - Overview
description:
Shop for the Gaggenau Vario 200 Series Gas Cooktop at Abt: http://www.abt.com/product/53306/Gaggenau-12-Inch-Stainless-Steel-Vario-Gas-Wok-Cooktop-VG232214CA.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=VG232214CA_20160901

Main Facts:
-Can be combined with the cooktops of the Vario 200 series for a harmonic unity
-Generous control panel for comfortable and secure operation
-Solid smooth-surface cast pan supports for easy and safe positioning of cookware

Cooking zones
-1 high output burner (560 – 2800 W) 9500 BTU suitable for pots up to max. ø 8 2/3.
-1 standard output burner (380 – 1900 W) 6500 BTU suitable for pots up to max. ø 8 2/3.

One-handed operation.

Cast-iron pan support with continuous grates.

Enameled burner caps.
